#: ../../guide-config-language.md:71
msgid "`prose_patterns`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../guide-config-language.md:73
msgid ""
"`prose_patterns` is a list of line-level regexes. A non-empty line is "
"treated as prose only if it matches at least one pattern."
msgstr ""

#: ../../guide-config-language.md:76
msgid ""
"If you leave `prose_patterns` empty, every non-empty line is treated as "
"prose unless it is excluded by `skip_patterns` or `skip_blocks`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../guide-config-language.md:79
msgid "`skip_patterns`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../guide-config-language.md:81
msgid ""
"`skip_patterns` is a list of line-level regexes. If a line matches any of"
" them, that line is excluded from checking."
msgstr ""

